<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="room-n">room <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ruːm;rʊm/    美 /ruːm;rum/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 房间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go out of a room 
走出房间</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 空间；余地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is little room to move in the crowd. 
人群中没有挪动的空间。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Would you kindly <strong>make room for</strong> the old lady? 
请你为这位老太太腾个地方好吗?</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is still much room for improvement.
还有很大改进的余地。</p><footer>2015 江苏书面表达</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>James took the magazines off the little table to make room <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the television.  （2010 天津改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. for  </p></div>